<item>
            <title>[LU-10112] FLR: Support DoM component</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10112</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the phase 1 of FLR, it will not support DoM in mirror layout of FLR. It has disabled to create such a layout from command line. It&apos;s simply not convenient to do it at this stage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;DoM+FLR will be working in the next phase of FLR project.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
